The suspense horror/dark fantasy story is set in Tokyo, which is haunted by mysterious "ghouls" who are devouring humans. People are gripped by the fear of these ghouls whose identities are masked in mystery. An ordinary college student named Kaneki encounters Rize, a girl who is an avid reader like him, at the café he frequents. Little does he realize that his fate will change overnight.
(Source: Anime News Network)
Mushoku Tensei: Isekai Ittara Honki Dasu

When a 34-year-old underachiever gets run over by a bus, his story doesn’t end there. Reincarnated in a new world as an infant, Rudeus will seize every opportunity to live the life he’s always wanted. Armed with new friends, some freshly acquired magical abilities, and the courage to do the things he’s always dreamed of, he’s embarking on an epic adventure—with all of his past experience intact!
(Source: Funimation, edited)
<i>Note: The anime pre-screened its 1st and 2nd episode starting on the 27th of December on the Nico Nico Live Broadcasting and D Anime Store services<i/>

He and she were enemies. Until he knew he had the same loneliness in a dichotomized world. They are cheap, strong, and never die. The ultimate life regeneration system "Arcadia" was born from teenage soldiers who fight by making full use of the complex regeneration <Respawn>. They were invincible boys and girls (children who transcended death) who died on the battlefield and revived. The forefront of the war in which the two great powers compete for hegemony. Akihito, a boy who leads a platoon as an ace of the United States Army, is ordered to collect confidential information that is inevitable to be wiped out because of his poor performance. However, Akihito, who has kept his companions in an unexpected battle and collapse, is isolated deep underground where complex regeneration <respawn> is impossible, along with his fateful nemesis, the elite girl Philia of the Federal Army. Two people who have opposite personalities and skills and have the worst compatibility will cooperate and aim to return to the ground. The story of the encounter and resonance between him and her who continued to die on the battlefield that never died begins!
<i>Notes: - Winner of the Gold Award in the 28th Dengeki Novel Prize.
Unmei de Musubareta Koibito......no Azatoi Imouto to Issen wo Koeteshimau, Ano Hi made

"If we reunite, let's be lovers"
That was the promise I made with my childhood friend, Mitsuha Mahiru a long time ago.
In the spring of my second year in high school, our fateful reunion happened. We exchanged our unchanging feelings and officially became a couple.
Just when I thought we could cohabitate blissfully at my place, another housemate - Mahiru's younger sister, Saya joined.
One night, I was kissed by Saya, who sneaked into my room.
"Shhh...be quiet. Let's keep this a secret"
From that moment, the cohabitation of three filled with secrecies began - till the day I eventually crossed the line with my lover's sister.
